## Entity Hierarchy

In BeeHero, `group_id` == `beekeeper_id`. This repo covers **Beekeeper groups only**.

```
group_id  (beekeeper)
  в””в”Җв”Җ yard_id
        в””в”Җв”Җ sensor_mac_address  (one sensor per hive)
              в””в”Җв”Җ gateway_mac_address  (sensors report via a gateway)
```

