### 2. Hive Updates Query (Athena вҖ” raw DB)

Queried via `hive_updates_query()` from `src/model_monitor/ingestion/`.
The FROM table depends on the query date вҖ” always use the helper, never hardcode.

#### Table Source Switch вҖ” `supervised_beeframes` vs `unified_bee_frames` (IMPORTANT)

| Date range | Table |
|---|---|
| date вүӨ 2026-03-09 | `data_lake_raw_data.supervised_beeframes` |
| date вүҘ 2026-03-10 | `data_lake_raw_data.unified_bee_frames` |

**Rule:** always call `raw_bee_frames_table(date)` from `src/model_monitor/ingestion/` вҖ” never hardcode either table name.

