### 3. Ground Truth (`data/temp_ground_truth/ground_truth_statuess_ca_2026.csv`)

Human-labelled model status per group per date. Source for `extraction_plan.py`.

| Column | Values | Description |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| `date` | `YYYY-MM-DD` | The evaluation date |
| `group_id` | int | Beekeeper group |
| `status` | `valid` / `invalid` / `needs_recalibration` | Human ground truth label |

**51 groups, 643 labelled dates** (as of 2026-03-26).

