## Layer 1 вҖ” sensor_group_segment

> **Full spec:** `skills/sensor_group_segment/spec/spec.txt`

### Implementation

| Phase | Function | File |
|-------|----------|------|
| Phase 1 вҖ” Feature Engineering | `compute()` | `src/model_monitor/metrics/sensor_group_segment.py` |
| Phase 2 вҖ” Grading | `grade()` | `src/model_monitor/metrics/sensor_group_segment.py` |

Thresholds: `skills/sensor_group_segment/config/thresholds.yaml` вҶ’ `metrics.sensor_group_segment.grading`

Output per sensor: `PASS` / `WARNING` / `FAIL` + `reason` string.

### Results Layout

```
data/results/sensor_group_segment/group_{id}/{date}/
    {id}_{date}_sensor_group_segment.parquet          вҶҗ per-sensor results
    {id}_{date}_sensor_group_segment_summary.parquet  вҶҗ mean metrics + grade counts per hive_size
data/results/sensor_group_segment/results.parquet     вҶҗ all groups/dates combined
```

### Skill Layout (`skills/sensor_group_segment/`)

```
skills/sensor_group_segment/
  spec/spec.txt               вҶҗ source of truth: logic, rules, thresholds rationale
  config/thresholds.yaml      вҶҗ all grading thresholds (never hardcode in code)
  config/extraction_plan.py   вҶҗ 51 groups, 643 dates, model names
  config/split_config.py      вҶҗ train/test split config (75/25, valid+invalid only)
  scripts/pull_samples.py     вҶҗ Step 1: Athena вҶ’ local Parquet
  scripts/run.py              вҶҗ Step 2: compute + grade вҶ’ result Parquet
  scripts/calibrate_thresholds.py вҶҗ calibrate thresholds from sensor physics
  scripts/create_split.py     вҶҗ create train/test symlinks + manifest
  notebooks/exploration.ipynb вҶҗ interactive data exploration
```

**Run order:**
```bash
source scripts/refresh_aws_credentials.sh
nohup python skills/sensor_group_segment/scripts/pull_samples.py > pull_log.txt 2>&1 &
python skills/sensor_group_segment/scripts/create_split.py
python skills/sensor_group_segment/scripts/run.py
```

