### Train/Test Split (for Layer 2)

Split manifest: `data/samples/split_manifest.csv`
- Valid + invalid only (needs_recalibration excluded from split)
- 75/25 stratified by status, sorted by (group_id, date)

| | Train | Test | Total |
|---|---|---|---|
| valid | 269 | 90 | 359 |
| invalid | 154 | 52 | 206 |
